Company Values


 



    Frédéric Villoutreix Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer



We are moving from a product focus to a focus on providing our customers with innovative, value-adding solutions, like the exacting properties that our RTL and papers for Lower Ignition Propensity (LIP) cigarettes bring to cigarette design.  









Reinventing
Ourselves
SWM has a remarkable history of accomplishment spanning nearly
five centuries. We are justifiably proud of that. But this is a new
world and a new time. So we have embarked on a new path and
transitioned to new ways of doing business. Our goal is not just to
survive, but also to thrive. We must constantly reinvent ourselves.
We need to be on the leading edge of innovation. We need to be
ahead of the curve and to always know the answer to "What's
next?"

            next >
          


Reinventing Ourselves

Collaborating with Customers—and One Another 

Our Vision, Our Aspiration







Collaborating with
Customers-and One Another
We have already initiated change to help us focus more globally,
expand capacity and markets, improve operations, build safer work
processes and pursue environmental certifications. We have
established a new performance culture. Today we are truly operating
as One Company, collaborating with one another around the world-and
working more closely than ever with our customers-bringing our
talent, our energy and our ingenuity to bear. We have placed our
customers at the heart of everything we do because by helping them
to solve their problems and succeed, we will do the same for
ourselves.

            next >
          


Reinventing Ourselves

Collaborating with Customers—and One Another 

Our Vision, Our Aspiration







Our Vision, Our
Aspiration
Our goal is to be the undisputed leader of engineered solutions
to the tobacco and fine paper industries. To achieve such an
ambitious goal we are building our success on four fronts:

By anticipating our customers' needs and working with them to
deliver valuable, highly differentiated solutions.
By using our vaunted technical expertise and operational
excellence to ensure high-performance products of superior quality
and reliability.
By building strength worldwide as regulatory trends drive
cigarettes to become more sophisticated in design and
performance.
By leveraging our technological and product-engineering
leadership to continually identify new opportunities and expand our
offerings.

We aspire to be the first choice for our customers, our
employees and our shareholders; we will be satisfied with nothing
less.

            next >
          


