	Villoutreix, Frederic 





	Mr. Frederic P. Villoutreix is no longer Chairman of the Board, Co-Chief Executive Officer of Schweitzer Mauduit International Inc., effective May 5, 2017. As current Chairman and Chief Executive Officer and former Chief Operating Officer, He brings a unified vision and depth of understanding of the operational, financial, and strategic elements of the Company to the Board. He also serves as the primary liaison between management and the Board and fills the core leadership role for both groups. His experience, both within the Company and in the various management positions and international assignments he held with his previous manufacturing-based employer, enhanced his ability to perform these functions.



